// `jackdaw::prelude`. The macro expands to code that references
// `bevy_enhanced_input` and `jackdaw_api` as direct crate paths,
// so you'll need to add both as dependencies in `Cargo.toml`
// (matching the versions jackdaw pins) before using it. Once
// jackdaw 0.4 ships on crates.io this boilerplate goes away.
